WEBVTT

00:01.454 --> 00:04.413
You want to use my love
to save your love?!

00:04.457 --> 00:06.590
Very well.
I'll spare his life.

00:06.633 --> 00:07.678
No!

00:07.721 --> 00:09.462
And take
yours instead.

00:09.505 --> 00:10.787
Pascale believes
you killed Queen Joan.

00:12.247 --> 00:13.647
See him to the dungeon.

00:13.684 --> 00:16.425
Tell me Landry's head is
on a pike somewhere.

00:16.469 --> 00:18.645
Landry, go see your daughter
before King Philip

00:18.689 --> 00:20.212
removes the chance
from your hands.

00:20.255 --> 00:22.301
Farewell,
my brothers.

00:22.344 --> 00:23.737
They killed my husband,

00:23.781 --> 00:25.783
they took my baby,
and they slit his throat.

00:25.826 --> 00:27.132
The Templars
will pay for this.

00:27.175 --> 00:28.742
Prince Louis.
You're the one who...

00:28.786 --> 00:29.961
Shh, shh!

00:30.004 --> 00:31.527
What's happened
to you?

00:31.571 --> 00:34.313
I'm no longer burdened
by troubled thoughts.

00:34.356 --> 00:37.055
You once swore loyalty
to the Templars.

00:37.098 --> 00:39.666
How can I trust you'll be loyal
to my father and I?

